\c 144
\s Dhavhidhi anokumbira kuti Jehovha amukundise, amuropafadze
\d Pisarema raDhavhidhi
\p
\v 1 Ngaarumbidzwe Jehovha, dombo rangu, anodzidzisa maoko angu kurwa, nemimwe yangu kufura.
\v 2 Unyoro hwangu, nenhare yangu, shongwe yangu yakakwirira, nomurwiri wangu; nhovo yangu, uye iye wandinovimba naye; anoisa vanhu vangu pasi pangu.
\p
\v 3 Jehovha, munhu chinyiko, zvamune hanya naye? Kana mwanakomana womunhu, zvamunomurangarira?
\v 4 Munhu akafanana nomweya; mazuva ake anenge mumvuri unopfuura.
\p
\v 5 Kotamisa kudenga-denga kwenyu Jehovha, muburuke; gunzvai makomo, apfungaire hutsi.
\v 6 Penyesai mheni, muvaparadze; furai miseve yenyu, muvavhunduse.
\v 7 Tandavadzai ruoko rwenyu muri kumusoro; ndisunungurei, mundirwire pamvura zhinji, naparuoko rwavatorwa.
\v 8 Avo vanotaura zvisina maturo nomuromo wavo, uye ruoko rwavo rworudyi ndirwo ruoko rworudyi rwenhema.
\p
\v 9 Mwari ndichakuimbirai rwiyo rutsva; ndichakuimbirai nziyo dzokurumbidza nomutengeranwa une hungiso dzine gumi.
\v 10 Ndimi munopa madzimambo kuponeswa, munorwira Dhavhidhi muranda wenyu pamunondo unokuvadza.
\p
\v 11 Ndisunungurei, mundirwire paruoko rwavatorwa, vanotaura zvisina maturo nomuromo wavo, uye ruoko rwavo rworudyi ndirwo ruoko rworudyi rwenhema.
\v 12 Vanakomana vedu vachava semiti yakakura kwazvo pautsva hwayo; uye vanasikana vedu samabwe ekona akavezwa sezvinovezerwa imba yamambo.
\v 13 Matura edu achazara nezviyo zvamarudzi ese; namakwai edu achabereka zvuru negumi rezvuru kumafuro edu.
\v 14 Nzombe dzedu dzichatakudzwa zvizhinji; hatingaputsirwi madziro, kana kubuda kundorwa, hakungavi nemhere inoridzwa panzira dzomumusha medu.
\v 15 Vanomufaro vanhu avo, vanoitirwa saizvozvo; vanomufaro vanhu avo, Mwari wavo ari Jehovha.
